              <h2 class="story-title">Project Overview</h2>
              <div class="story-text">
                <p style="font-size:1.125rem;">Roskey's Computer Literacy and Beyond is a Port Huron nonprofit on a mission to bridge the digital divide for seniors. They offer free classes on everything from basic computer skills to online safety — and they needed a website that their audience could actually use.</p>
                <p style="margin-top:1rem;">We designed the site with accessibility as the top priority. Large text, clear navigation, high contrast, and an approachable design that doesn't intimidate less tech-savvy visitors. The result is a website that serves its community as thoughtfully as the organization itself.</p>
