                  The Challenge
                </h3>
                <p style="color:var(--muted-foreground);line-height:1.7;font-weight:300;">Build a website for an audience that may struggle with technology — seniors who are learning computer basics. Every design decision needed to reduce friction and build confidence, not add complexity.</p>
