                <p style="color:var(--muted-foreground);line-height:1.7;font-weight:300;">Prioritized accessibility at every level — large clickable areas, minimal navigation depth, approachable language, testimonials from past students, and a warm visual design that feels welcoming rather than overwhelming.</p>
